Default replication factor for Hadoo is 3


Hadoop Distributions 
1. Cloudra
2. Hortonworks

For this training we are using Cloudra.

Defining lambda in Python

HDFS :
Create a folder : hdfs dfs -mkdir /hadooptraining
Put (to upload a file to hdfs system) cmd : hdfs dfs -put first.txt /hadooptraining
To see the content of file : hdfs dfs -cat /hadooptraining/first.txt
Copying file from one folder to another : hdfs dfs -cp /hadooptraining/first.txt /hadooptraining1

